    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<section class=\"description\">\n<p>The following article outlines a short checklist of questions to ask and steps to take before opening an upgrade ticket. By taking a moment to go through this checklist before opening a request, you are ensuring the fastest possible resolution for your particular issue.</p>\n</section>\n<section id=\"resolution\">\n<h2>Resolution</h2>\n<div>\n<p id=\"aui_3_4_0_1_1164\">For each ticket, please attach your <code>portal-ext.properties</code> file as well as the output of the <em>patching-tool info</em> command specific to the environment.</p>\n<p>For upgrade tickets specifically, <strong><em>please work through the following checklist and include the resulting information when you create a ticket:</em></strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>For ease, upgrade should be conducted with a Liferay provided bundle. This is to reduce the resources needed to upgrade if the existing app server is resource-heavy.</li>\n<li>If performing an upgrade, the upgraded should first be conducted in lower environments, starting with Dev/QA. Upgrades need to be tested before moving into Production.</li>\n<li>The Portal upgrade should be <em>out of the box</em> (OOTB) and should not include any customizations.</li>\n<li>Have you followed our <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360018425791\">Upgrade Instructions</a> and <a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360018075472\">Upgrading to Permission Algorithm 6: Best practices</a>?</li>\n<li>In case of an upgrade failure, everything needs to be reverted back to the previous point.</li>\n<li>Have you installed the latest core fix packs and upgrade fix pack (if available)?</li>\n<li>If you have already attempted the upgrade please provide us with\n<ol type=\"a\">\n<li>Complete old <code>portal-ext.properties</code>\n</li>\n<li>Complete new <code>portal-ext.properties</code>\n</li>\n<li>Patching-tool output from the old server if available</li>\n<li>Patching-tool output from the new server</li>\n<li>A copy of the pre-upgrade database (FTP)</li>\n<li>A copy of your data folder and image gallery if in a different location (FTP)</li>\n<li>A copy of any exceptions generated during the process</li>\n<li>A copy of the full logs generated during the upgrade\n<ul>\n<li>This log should include the update processes</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section id=\"additionalInformation\">\n<h2>Additional Information</h2>\n<div>\n<p><em>Want help with your upgrade?</em></p>\n<p>Liferay Global Services offers solutions to fit your needs. <a href=\"https://www.liferay.com/consulting\">Please contact us for a free consultation</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</section>"
      },
